                                                                  By KernelFl00d
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ddos2track is an opensource tool that protect your server from DDoS Attacks.

Options
-----------

- Detect DDoS and send you an email message with DDoS Information.

- Redirect DDoS Traffic to a honeypot and analyze request, then save all requests in a log file.

- Block Attackers IP Addresses and map all the IP Addresses belonging to the attacker botnet.

- You can redirect DDoS traffic to attackers IP Addresses and DoS their connection ;)


Default Port to protect: 80
Default Port to run honeypot: 8089

If you want to change, please change it in source code


INSTALLING
------------
chmod 777 INSTALL.sh && sh INSTALL.sh


USAGE
------------
./ddos2track


